      </table></td>
  </tr>
</table><table id="cjNavItem2" style="background:url(../images/menu_bg1.gif); position:absolute; top:-1000em;" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td height="2" id="dropdown" ><img src="../images/menu_line01.gif" height="2" /></td></tr><tr><td height="20" id="dropdown" ><a href="project-1.htm">計劃簡介 </a></td></tr><tr><td height="2" id="dropdown" ><img src="../images/menu_line01.gif" height="2" /></td></tr><tr><td height="20" id="dropdown" ><a href="project-2.htm">典藏特色 </a></td></tr><tr><td height="2" id="dropdown" ><img src="../images/menu_line01.gif" height="2" /></td></tr><tr><td height="20" id="dropdown" ><a href="project-3.htm">執行架構 </a></td></tr><tr><td height="2" id="dropdown" ><img src="../images/menu_line01.gif" height="2" /></td></tr><tr><td height="20" id="dropdown" ><a href="project-4.htm">計畫典藏數位化流程</a></td></tr><tr><td height="2" id="dropdown" ><img src="../images/menu_line01.gif" height="2" /></td></tr><tr><td height="20" id="dropdown" ><a href="members.htm">成員介紹</a></td></tr></table><table id="cjNavItem3" style="background:url(../images/menu_bg1.gif); position:absolute; top:-1000em;" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr><td height="2" id="dropdown" ><img src="../images/menu_line01.gif" width="100%" height="2" /></td></tr><tr><td height="20" id="dropdown" ><a href="about-2.htm">台灣白話字發展簡介</a></td></tr><tr><td height="2" id="dropdown" ><img src="../images/menu_line01.gif" width="100%" height="2" /></td></tr><tr><td height="20" id="dropdown" ><a href="about-3.htm">巴克禮牧師與《台灣教會公報》</a></td></tr><tr><td height="2" id="dropdown" ><img src="../images/menu_line01.gif" width="100%" height="2" /></td></tr><tr><td height="20" id="dropdown" ><a href="about-4.htm">廈門話字典-杜嘉德</a></td></tr><tr><td height="2" id="dropdown" ><img src="../images/menu_line01.gif" width="100%" height="2" /></td></tr><tr><td height="20" id="dropdown" ><a href="about-5.htm">白話字教學-打馬字</a></td></tr><tr><td height="2" id="dropdown" ><img src="../images/menu_line01.gif" width="